name: Mao Ze Dong 100th Year Birthday Anniversary Pocket Watch
description:
Get your own piece of history!

On the face of the pocket watch is Chairman Mao and his arm waves with the second hand. The back of the watch has a temple engraved along with "Mao Ze Dong 100th Year Birthday Anniversary 1893 - 1993"

Please use the contact link and provide your email address if you would like to see more photos.

name: Guys & Dolls Original Cast Album
description: The beloved musical, Guys & Dolls, is captured on this record including all the favourites - take back your mink, If I were a bell and luck be a lady. This statement piece makes a funky addition to a lounge, bedroom or studio. Frame the record or hang the piece and let the memories of Nathan Detroit, Miss Adelaide, Sky Masterson and Sarah Brown flood back!
